            <title>[SPARK-5751] Flaky test: o.a.s.sql.hive.thriftserver.HiveThriftServer2Suite sometimes times out</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-5751</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The &quot;Test JDBC query execution&quot; test case times out occasionally, all other test cases are just fine. The failure output only contains service startup command line without any log output. Guess somehow the test case misses the log file path.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
